  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 - \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel Lack - Rail Service Impact in the Upcoming Days - Railway Station Officers Association",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Most of the people are currently using the rail transport service due to fuel shortage and increase in bus fares. Rail service will be affected in the coming days due to fuel shortage.",
        "If the train service is disrupted, the public transport service will come to a complete standstill.",
        "We acknowledge that fuel shortages are a major problem facing the people of the country.",
        "A major problem in the availability of fuel has affected the service of the Railway Department, Railway Station Officers and other employees to the service community.",
        "Although it has been mentioned that priority will be given to public servants in refueling at petrol stations, it is a matter of concern that the focus is not on the distribution of fuel to railway servicemen as rail service has become an essential service.",
        "At present most of the people use the train service."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Fuel Lack - Rail Service",
          "label": "PERSON"
        },
